---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Results That Matter" description="Review David Glass's proven track record of infrastructure improvements, fiscal responsibility, and managed growth in Bastrop County.">
  
  <div class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-navy text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">Results That Matter</h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-light text-warm-gray leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        What we have accomplished together in Precinct 4 and across Bastrop County. We do not just make plans, we deliver outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white relative">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <!-- Roads and Infrastructure -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="mb-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy inline-block border-b-4 border-gold pb-2 mb-4">Roads & Infrastructure</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-near-black max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Decades of deferred maintenance and unprecedented county growth demand decisive action. Here is how we are keeping Bastrop County moving.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Targeted Mill & Overlay</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Dozens of miles of county roads have been completely rebuilt or resurfaced using sustainable mill and overlay techniques to stretch every tax dollar further.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Critical Bridge Replacements</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Identified and secured funding to repair or replace aging bridges across Precinct 4, prioritizing school bus routes and emergency response paths.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Comprehensive Drainage</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Invested heavily in clearing and rebuilding drainage channels along county right-of-ways to prevent road washout and protect private property.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Budget and Fiscal Responsibility -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="mb-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy inline-block border-b-4 border-gold pb-2 mb-4">Budget & Fiscal Accountability</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-near-black max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Every dollar the county spends comes directly from the people who live here. We manage it accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-navy text-white rounded p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-3">No-Nonsense Budgeting</h3>
            <p class="text-warm-gray leading-relaxed text-lg mb-0">Applying business principles to the county budget to root out waste, demand efficiency from departments, and deliver fundamental services without defaulting to tax hikes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy text-white rounded p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-3">Responsible Fleet Management</h3>
            <p class="text-warm-gray leading-relaxed text-lg mb-0">Re-evaluating county equipment lifecycle and purchasing procedures to save taxpayers hundreds of thousands of dollars over the long term.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Growth Management and Water -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="mb-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy inline-block border-b-4 border-gold pb-2 mb-4">Growth Management</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-near-black max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Bastrop County is a prime target for developers. We are ensuring development serves the community, rather than exploiting it.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Demanding High Standards</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Holding developers accountable to strict subdivision rules, ensuring they pay for the infrastructure required by their developments, not existing taxpayers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Water Security</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Leveraging decades of water infrastructure experience to ensure new subdivisions have secured sustainable water rights before ground is broken.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border border-warm-gray/50 rounded shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Protecting Property Rights</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Striking the delicate balance between managing subdivision density and protecting the fundamental rights of long-time Bastrop County landowners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Investment -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy inline-block border-b-4 border-gold pb-2 mb-4">Community Investment</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-near-black max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Supporting the partnerships that make Bastrop County a great place to live and work.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border-l-4 border-navy rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Economic Development</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Working with the Elgin Economic Development Corporation and surrounding municipalities to attract responsible, high-paying jobs to the county.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-gray/10 border-l-4 border-navy rounded p-6 shadow-sm">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Emergency Preparedness</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black">Securing resources for local volunteer fire departments and emergency medical services to drastically improve response times in rural Precinct 4.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
